169
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:51,010
Untuk bunga menjadi mekar,

170
00:15:51,420 --> 00:15:53,130
dia perlu ditiup angin...

171
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:55,050
dan ditimpa hujan.

172
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:06,440
Awak tahu di mana Cik Jang?

173
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:09,780
Dia belum pulang.

174
00:16:09,810 --> 00:16:11,700
Ada apa-apa yang berlaku
semasa awak keluar?

175
